    return tf.nn.softmax(x, axis=axis)

body:
@SidJain1412 I think you need to search the location of filename `tensorflow_backend.py` which should be within a sub-directory of Python root path. Open the file with an editor, when change the line below from:

```sh
    return tf.nn.softmax(x, axis=axis)
```

into:
```sh
    return tf.nn.softmax(x)    # Just remove the second argument will be okay
```
